Defeat many Worms in the North Downs and Ram Dúath

Legend has it that the Enemy spent long ages devising the great breed of Dragons that have bedeviled Middle-earth. Worms are among the lesser forms that were discarded along the way -- but they are still deadly foes, and more common than their greater kin by far.
